\[\mathrm{d}(\|x_{t}-x_{t}^{\circ}\|^{2})=-2\left\langle x_{t}-x_{t}^{\circ}, \nabla U(x_{t})-\nabla U(x_{t}^{\circ})\right\rangle\leq 2L\,\|x_{t}-x_{t}^{ \circ}\|^{2}\,.\]

