\[\mathbb{E}[\|x_{t}-x_{t}^{\circ}\|^{2}]\leq e^{2Lt}\,\mathbb{E}[\|x_{0}-x_{0}^ {\circ}\|^{2}]=e^{2Lt}\,W_{2}^{2}(p,q)\lesssim W_{2}^{2}(p,q)\,,\]

recalling that \(t\leq T_{\mathsf{corr}}\lesssim 1/L\) by hypothesis. 

